+```css
+ul::before{
+  /* Use calc() to offset the top slightly */
+  inset-block-start: calc(anchor(end) + .1lh);
+  inset-inline-start: anchor(start);
+  inset-inline-end: anchor(end);
+}
+```
+
+Add a height and other visual styles.
+
+```css
+ul::before{
+  block-size: .25lh;
+  background: red;
+}
